text: Gamvik, or Gáŋgaviikka, is a municipality in Norway's northernmost county, Finnmark. Settlements include Mehamn. ==Administration== The municipal council is elected until late 2027. *6 council members are from Labour party https://www.nrk.no/valg/2023/resultat/fylke/56/5626. NRK.no.
